NOTE ON INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY

The MIT license above applies ONLY to the original source code of this Foundry
VTT system (JavaScript, CSS, templates, and configuration).

This is an unofficial, non-commercial fan project. "Witchcraft and Wizardry"
and the surrounding setting are derived from J.K. Rowling's Wizarding World.
All names, trademarks, and copyrights of that setting belong to their
respective owners.

The compendium content shipped with this system (spell names and descriptions
under packs/) is transcribed from the community Core Rulebook (v1.4) and the
broader Wizarding World. It is included solely for private, non-commercial use,
in the same spirit as that rulebook, which states it "cannot be reproduced for
the intent of retail sale or personal gain." Nothing here may be used for
retail sale or personal gain.

All artwork referenced by this system comes from Foundry VTT's built-in icon
library; no third-party art is redistributed in this repository.
